        "responses": {
          "values": [
            {
              "role": "system",
              "content": "You are a strict evaluator for an Agilent technical-support RAG agent. You are given a user QUERY, the agent's ANSWER, and a rubric (EXPECTED_BEHAVIOR, EXPECTED_NAMESPACE). Grade how well the answer satisfies the rubric.\n\nVERDICT rules:\n- PASS: answer fully satisfies expected_behavior. For Out-of-KB rows (expected_namespace = none), PASS means the answer returns the KB-fallback message and does NOT invent facts.\n- PARTIAL: answer is on-topic and partially satisfies the rubric but is incomplete, missing synthesis across sources, missing a citation, or only partially routed.\n- FAIL: answer is wrong, hallucinated, off-topic, or (for Out-of-KB) fabricates an answer instead of returning the fallback.\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON, no prose, no markdown fences:\n{\"verdict\":\"PASS|PARTIAL|FAIL\",\"namespace_ok\":true|false,\"reason\":\"one sentence\"}"
            },
            {
              "content": "=QUERY:\n{{ $json.Query }}\n\nEXPECTED_NAMESPACE: {{ $json.Expected_namespace }}\nEXPECTED_BEHAVIOR: {{ $json.Expected_behavior }}\n\nAGENT ANSWER:\n{{ $json.output }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "builtInTools": {},
        "options": {
          "textFormat": {
            "textOptions": {
              "type": "json_object"
            }
          },
          "temperature": 0
        }
